{"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"1-Create-HTML-Page","text":"1. Create HTML Page","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every website have few pages associated with it, lets see how to make a HTMLPage using HTMLKit"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["   struct FirstPage: HTMLPage {","","        \/\/\/ Your HTMLContent","        var htmlContent: [HTMLBlock] {","","          Heading(.h1, \"Random Image\")","","          Image(src: \"https:\/\/picsum.photos\/200\/300\", alt: \"Test\")","   ","          HorizontalRule()","       }","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Create a struct and implement the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/HTMLSwiftKit\/documentation\/HTMLSwiftKit\/HTMLPage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, and you are good to start building your page."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"2-Create-CSS","type":"heading","text":"2. Create CSS"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Now just like every normal HTML page you need to give some CSS to it, so HTMLSwiftKit covers that too."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["   struct BasicCSS: CSSBlock {","   ","     var cssType: CSSType = .custom","   ","     var content: [CSSModifier] {","         Border(5, border: .dotted, color: \"orange\")","         BackgroundColor(color: \"yellow\")","         FontSize(22)","         Color(\"Red\")","         Padding(200)","     }","   }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a struct implement the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/HTMLSwiftKit\/documentation\/HTMLSwiftKit\/CSSBlock","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol and provide the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and start adding your styling modifiers."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","te